<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    .c1 {
      width: 1285.01px;
      height: 508px;
      position: absolute;
      padding-top: 10%;
      left: 30px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 0;
      border-radius: 18px;
      opacity: 1;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .c1 img {
      width: 636px;
      height: 472px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .accordion-container {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .accordion {
      width: 587.01px;
      padding: 24px 24px 24px 0px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .accordion-header {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 36.4px;
      text-align: left;
      color: #434A57;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .accordion-content {
      display: none;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 36.4px;
      text-align: left;
      color: #576071;
    }

    .accordion.active .accordion-header {
      color: #F1592A;
    }

    .accordion.active .accordion-content {
      display: block;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="c1">
    <img src="/assets/img/hero/hero.jpg" alt="Description of image">
    <div class="accordion-container">
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-header">Unlocking Digital Empowerment</div>
        <div class="accordion-content">By mastering digital tools like Canva, website building, social media, and mobile skills, women can unlock endless possibilities for personal and professional growth.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-header">Unlocking Digital Empowerment</div>
        <div class="accordion-content">By mastering digital tools like Canva, website building, social media, and mobile skills, women can unlock endless possibilities for personal and professional growth.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-header">Unlocking Digital Empowerment</div>
        <div class="accordion-content">By mastering digital tools like Canva, website building, social media, and mobile skills, women can unlock endless possibilities for personal and professional growth.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-header">Unlocking Digital Empowerment</div>
        <div class="accordion-content">By mastering digital tools like Canva, website building, social media, and mobile skills, women can unlock endless possibilities for personal and professional growth.</div>
      </div>
     
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-header').forEach(header => {
      header.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const accordion = header.parentElement;
        accordion.classList.toggle('active');
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
